4–202 of the Criminal Procedure Article:
[(i) Abduction;
(ii) Kidnapping;]
(I) (III) ANY CRIME PUNISHABLE BY LIFE IMPRISONMENT;
[(iii)] (II) (IV) Second degree murder;
[(iv)] (III) (V) Manslaughter, except involuntary manslaughter;
[(v)] (IV) (VI) Second degree rape;
