WES MOORE, Governor Ch. 609
[(xvi)] (VIII) (XIV) A violation of [§ 4–203,] § 4–204[, § 4–404, or §
4–405] of the Criminal Law Article;
[(5)] (4) A child who previously has been convicted as an adult of a
